    <title>hexo+Github pages</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2017/06/01/hexo-Github-pages/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2017/06/01/hexo-Github-pages/</id>
    <published>2017-06-01T10:50:24.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-06-01T10:50:53.101Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Hexo-Github-pages"><a href="#Hexo-Github-pages" class="headerlink" title="Hexo + Github pages"></a>Hexo + Github pages</h2><blockquote>
<p>安装hexo</p>
</blockquote>
<figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ cd d:/hexo</div><div class="line"><span class="comment">//随便那个建个hexo文件夹</span></div><div class="line">$ npm install hexo-cli -g  </div><div class="line"><span class="comment">//hexo-cli脚手架工作</span></div><div class="line">$ hexo init blog  </div><div class="line"><span class="comment">//初始化blog项目</span></div><div class="line">$ cd blog</div><div class="line">$ npm install</div><div class="line"><span class="comment">//安装相关依赖 有可能全都默认装好了</span></div><div class="line">$ hexo g</div><div class="line"><span class="comment">// 或者hexo generate 生成静态文件 public</span></div><div class="line">$ hexo s</div><div class="line"><span class="comment">// 或者hexo server，可以在http://localhost:4000/ 查看默认效果</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<p>新增</p>
</blockquote>
<figure class="highlight coffeescript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="string">"postName"</span> <span class="comment">#新建文章</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>然后在blog目录下找到source/_posts/postname.md<br>编辑器打开这个文件</p>
<h2 id="默认格式"><a href="#默认格式" class="headerlink" title="默认格式"></a>默认格式</h2><p>title: hello hexo<br>date: 2017-06-01 14:14:38</p>
<h2 id="tags-html"><a href="#tags-html" class="headerlink" title="tags: html"></a>tags: html</h2><p>以下就是要写的内容（markdown语法书写（百度））</p>
<hr>
<blockquote>
<p>主题安装</p>
</blockquote>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo clean</div><div class="line">//这个命令是删掉之前生成的public文件夹</div><div class="line">$ git clone https://github.com/litten/hexo-theme-yilia.git themes/yilia</div><div class="line">//https://github.com/litten/hexo-theme-yilia.git 主题的仓库地址</div><div class="line">//themes/yilia 在blog目录下以themes/主题名格式生成文件夹</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">//应用主题去blog根目录下_config.yml文件去理改，下面这个字段</div><div class="line"># Extensions</div><div class="line">## Plugins: https://hexo.io/plugins/</div><div class="line">## Themes: https://hexo.io/themes/</div><div class="line">theme: apollo</div><div class="line">//一般不用更新主题，clone过来一般都是最新的，要更新就cd 主题文件</div><div class="line">$ git pull</div><div class="line">//主题的选项和修改，自己看人Github仓库的文档</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<p>Github pages</p>
</blockquote>
<p><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/0ddd2851a42f554c118a048eca3c8b32_b.png" alt="enter description here"></p>
<hr>
<p><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/f1ceb7c4c768a5141083ce09cbf1a340_b.png" alt="enter description here"></p>
<hr>
<p>上面就是你的Github账户下创建个仓库，名字必须按格式写</p>
<hr>
<blockquote>
<p>部署</p>
</blockquote>
<p>在_config.yml文件的</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"># Deployment</div><div class="line">## Docs: https://hexo.io/docs/deployment.html</div><div class="line">deploy:</div><div class="line">  type: git</div><div class="line">  repository: https://github.com/Pengyang7568/Pengyang7568.github.io</div><div class="line">  branch: master</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><strong>repository</strong> 这个是你的仓库地址</p>
<p>然后在执行</p>
<figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</div><div class="line"><span class="comment">//部署的插件</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>执行</p>
<figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo g</div><div class="line">$ hexo d</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-afc855fbbb24c435dde04ae2bce57711_b.png" alt="正确上传效果就是这样"></p>
<p>  正确上传效果就是上面，最好是下个Github的客服端，没有客服端会在命令行让你输账户，密码，有客服端会弹个窗口输</p>
<p>  上传成功后，你就可以访问<strong>Pengyang7568.github.io</strong> 前面换成你的用户名就可以</p>
<p>  每次要写了新文章，就</p>
<figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo clean</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">$ hexo new <span class="string">"文章名字"</span></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">$ hexo g</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">$ hexo s <span class="comment">//本地看看效果</span></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">$ hexo d <span class="comment">//部署上去</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>然后就访问地址就可以看到了</p>
<p>还有一些插件，自己去官网研究，比如说评论插件，markdown自己学，很简单或者下个markdown编辑器，写好了复制进去<br>苹果干这些事天生有优势，Git是要装的，你们应该学了撒</p>
]]></content>
    
